The Emotions Evoked by Music

Within this interactive map, music samples are plotted along the 13 dimensions of self-reported emotional experience evoked by music across cultures (US and China). Each letter corresponds to a music track. Float over to play. Double click to reveal source (if available). Click and drag to rearrange.
